message: /* Career */ Revised section to include more accurate details on the facts surrounding the incidents and make it more respectful to Mr. Young.
fixed the website URL in the bio box
/* Career */ made a couple minor edits to revise my update.
Corrected citation error from previous edit.
Changed career section to include the important information but make it more respectful. Also updated the URL in the box to the correct official website.
Contesting article content that is against Wikipedia's policies about biographies of living people.

/* Publications */ Added an additional book by D. Gary Young.
Added published papers under the publications section
